Hello [~rli@atlassian.com] 

I unzipped the Language Pack (bitbucket-language-pack-ja_JP-8.19.0.rc4-202403032039.jar) on Bitbucket 8.19.6 and checked the property file. As shown below, multiple entries are listed on a single line.　 There are several such lines.
{code:java|title=jira-integration-plugin_ja_JP.properties}
dialog.field.type=\u30bf\u30a4\u30d7:dialog.heading.description=\u8aac\u660e{code}
I modified this file, as you can see below.
{code:java}
dialog.field.type=\u30bf\u30a4\u30d7:
dialog.heading.description=\u8aac\u660e{code}
I recreated the jar file and tested it. The problem was solved. I hope Atlassian will implement this fix in the next release.

Best Regards,

